snippet.title: Celebrities Who Defended Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Celebrities Who Defended Amber Heard
Subscribe To Landon Production: https://www.youtube.com/user/LandonProduction
Watch Our Recent Videos Here: https://bit.ly/3mMfO8g

Amber Heard is once again making headline as 1.3 million people sign a petition to remove her from Aquaman 2 following Johnny Depp losing the libel case and being removed from Fantastic Beasts 2. With this news though, many celebrities have come forward to defend Amber. These are the Celebrities Who Defended Amber Heard right here on Top 10 Beyond The Screen!
